    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Miklós Oláh to Lajos Pekry (Worms, 16 June 1545)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">The King has ordered Báthori in a letter to be patient
                            regarding the collection of the customs duties, and he should not
                            generate further injustices, he should wait for the legal redress that
                            Várday will write about instead. Pekry should make sure that Báthori
                            gets the letter as soon as possible. He also thanks him for being
                            available to help him in Slavonia.</p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Magnifice Domine, Amice Observandissime, salutem et nostri
                    commendationem! </p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Ea, quae Magnifica Dominatio Vestra nobis scripserat, intelleximus.
                    Nostrum patrocinium, ut nullis aliis ita ne in his quidem Magnificae
                    Dominationis Vestrae negotiis apud <persName>regiam maiestatem</persName>,
                    dominum nostrum clementissimum defuit. Mandavit sua maiestas his litteris, quae
                    ad Magnificam Dominationem Vestram cum praesentibus perlatae sunt, domino
                        <persName>Andreae de Bathor</persName>, ut ratione telonei patientiam
                    habeat, neque novas iniurias suscitet, sed quiete exspectet iuris revisionem,
                    quam dominus <persName>locumtenens</persName><note xml:id="note.1">Pál
                        Várday.</note> praescribet. Magnifica Dominatio Vestra curet, quamprimum
                    litteras suae maiestatis ad ipsum dominum <persName>Bathory</persName> expedire,
                    et seipsam mandato suae maiestatis accommodare.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Quod autem scribit Magnifica Dominatio Vestra recepta pristina
                        sanitate<note xml:id="note.2">In Ep. 654. Pekry does not mention his state
                        of health.<ref>olahus.tei.15450521_1</ref></note> se in Sclavoniam
                    profecturam, et ibi hominibus nostris auxilio adfuturam, id nobis gratum est.
                    Eamque rogamus, ut cum illuc venerit, ope sua homines nostros iuvare non
                    praetermittat. Nos hunc laborem Magnificae Dominationis Vestrae maioribus rebus
                    reponemus. Quam bene valere optamus.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.4">Datum <placeName>Vormatiae</placeName> 16. mensis Iunii 1545.</p>
                <p xml:id="p.5">
                    <seg type="signature">
                        <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Nicolaus Olahus episcopus
                            Zagrabiensis</add>
                    </seg>
                </p>
                <p xml:id="p.6">
                    <add corresp="Olahus" type="insert">Litteras regias ad dominum
                            <persName>Bathori</persName> sonantes misi ad dominum
                            <persName>Strigoniensem</persName>.<note xml:id="note.3">Pál
                            Várday.</note> Ipse enim eas citius ad ipsum dominum Bathori mittere
                        poterit.</add>
                </p>
                <pb/>
            </div>
            <div style="handwritten" type="verso" xml:id="d.2">
                <head>On the outer side:</head>
                <p xml:id="p.7">Magnifico domino Ludovico Pekry de Petrowyna etc. domino et amico
                    observandissimo.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
